Vocals & Verses is an event dedicated to showcasing the finest spoken word and live music in the UK.

Paving the way of the big artists of tomorrow

Providing high quality from beginning to end and the talent captivates you right up until the final few minutes of the event. For many artists our stage has been part of the journey to mainstream success examples include JP Cooper, Jacob Banks, Shakka, Cythnia Erivo and Ray BLK.

Relationships are born beyond the stage

Creates an environment that people of different backgrounds and walks of life come together with a common purpose and provides the perfect platform for people to network with others with similar passions.
